3. PERFORMANCE SPECIFICATIONS

3.1 End-to-End Latency Budget

```
Process Stage                    Max Latency   Safety Critical?
---------------------------------------------------------------
Sensor Acquisition               2ms           No
Sensor Processing                5ms           No
Fusion & World Model Update      15ms          Yes
Prediction (10s horizon)         20ms          No
Quantum Decision                 50ms          Yes
Kernel Scheduling                1ms           Yes
Actuator Command                 5ms           Yes
Physical Response                10ms          N/A
---------------------------------------------------------------
TOTAL (Perception to Action)     108ms         -
```

3.2 Computational Performance

· Total AI Performance: 200 TOPS (int8) / 50 TFLOPS (fp16)
· Memory Bandwidth: 400 GB/s system-wide
· Storage I/O: 8 GB/s sequential, 1M IOPS random
· Network I/O: 100 Gbps external, 400 Gbps internal

3.3 Power Management

```
Power Domain          Typical      Peak        Management Strategy
--------------------------------------------------------------------
