5. DEVELOPMENT & DEPLOYMENT SPECIFICATIONS

5.1 Software Development Kit

· Programming Languages: C++20 (safety), Rust (systems), Python (AI/ML)
· Simulation Environment: Digital twin with photorealistic sensor simulation
· Testing Framework: SIL/HIL/VIL toolchain with fault injection
· CI/CD Pipeline: GitOps with safety gate approvals

5.2 OTA Update Specifications

· Update Size: Up to 50 GB for full system update
· Bandwidth Requirements: Minimum 100 Mbps for critical updates
· Update Time: <20 minutes for non-critical, <5 minutes for safety
· Rollback Mechanism: A/B partitioning with automatic fallback
· Security: End-to-end signed with quantum-safe certificates

5.3 Compliance Matrix

```
