6. PHYSICAL & ENVIRONMENTAL SPECIFICATIONS

6.1 Hardware Platform

· Form Factor: 3U ruggedized server chassis
· Dimensions: 400mm × 300mm × 150mm
· Weight: <15 kg
· Cooling: Liquid cold plate + redundant fans
· Power Input: 48V DC nominal (36-72V range)
· Operating Temperature: -40°C to +85°C ambient
· Vibration: MIL-STD-810H Method 514.8
· EMC/EMI: CISPR 25 Class 5, ISO 11452-2

6.2 Connectors & Interfaces

· Sensor Interfaces: 12× MIPI CSI-2, 8× Automotive Ethernet (1000BASE-T1)
· Network Interfaces: 2× 6G RF, 4× 5G, 2× WiFi 7, 2× GPS/GNSS
· Vehicle Bus: 4× CAN FD, 2× FlexRay, 1× Automotive Ethernet (10GBASE-T1)
· Debug/Service: 2× USB 4.0, 1× JTAG, 1× RS-232

