8. APPENDIX: GLOSSARY OF TERMS

· QDI: Quantum Decision Interface - Quantum-enhanced optimization layer
· ARTK: AI-Native Real-Time Kernel - Safety-certified microkernel
· PSG: Proactive Sensor Grid - Multi-modal sensor array
· MFE: Multi-modal Fusion Engine - World model constructor
· PQC: Post-Quantum Cryptography - Quantum-resistant algorithms
· SOTIF: Safety Of The Intended Functionality (ISO 21448)
· ODD: Operational Design Domain - Defined conditions for autonomy
· V2X: Vehicle-to-Everything communication
· MEC: Multi-access Edge Computing
· QKD: Quantum Key Distribution

