END OF TECHNICAL SPECIFICATION

This document defines the comprehensive technical requirements for the Quantum-6G Vehicle Operating System. All specifications are subject to change based on technological advancements, regulatory requirements, and market conditions. Implementation must follow the defined safety and security processes throughout the product lifecycle.
